channel.description:
Here we strive to become one of the best servers out there. We know how important it is for you to enjoy your time on a private server. So today we bring you Vomero. A friendly and fun filled community. Here we accept everyone who is willing to come and have a great time. Do you think you can do that? Who know until you try it yourself. Come join Vomero!
